\pard\tx720\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Yes, both graphs rise together from 1980 to the mid 2000s. However,  disaster counts level off towards roughly after 2000 while temperatures keep rising so the relationship might not be entirely correlated.\
